xul-ext-configuration-mania (24.0.0-1nano) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release
    - Versioning rule has changed to semver-based. So this version is 24.0.0
      (not 1.24.xxxxxxxxxx) (issue#229)
    - Firefox 38-44 support has been dropped. (issue #223)
    - Search bar on the panel has been added (issue#226)
    - Configuration Mania is now in-content panel only. (issue#225)
    - "Browser"->"Page control"->"Hardware acceleration"->"Enable Off Main
      Thread Compositing (OMTC)" has been marked as obsolete since Firefox 48
      (issue #222).

