xul-ext-configuration-mania (1.23.2016051501-1nano) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release
  * Supporting decoder options in "Browser"->"Multimedia" has been updated (issue #221):
    - "Enable Window Media Foundation" has been marked as obsolete since Firefox 42 (ref Bug 1185782)
    - "Enable Window Media Foundation" which requires Firefox 44 has also been added (ref Bug 1234092)
    - "Enable FFmpeg" has been added and requires Firefox 44 (ref Bug 1214932)
    - "Enable built-in FFVPX" has been added and requires marked as Firefox 45 (ref Bug 1240630)
    - "Enable Gecko Media Plugins (GMPs)" has been added and marked as requires Firefox 44 (ref Bug 1214932)
    - "Enable Apple MP4" has been added (ref Bug 1209388)
  * "Debug"->"Disable popup auto hide." has been added (issue #220)
  * "Browser"->"Other"->"View source with external editor" is now enabled even if "View source in a new tab" is checked (issue #213)

 -- Christopher Roy Bratusek <nano@jpberlin.de>  Wed, 18 May 2016 20:14:56 +0200

